{"tid":2440794,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"控經理人公司欠薪 YouTuber 「Ming仔」勝訴獲賠逾151萬元","createTime":"2021-03-10T08:01:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T08:07:17.000Z","uid":131875,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8e3ed51210cca9f9601cc5fc8ded79ad9546875c","tid":2440794,"uid":131875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:01:42.000Z","msg":"有香港初代YouTuber始祖之稱的梁嘉銘（Ming仔），4年前入稟控告經理人公司Viral Digital Studio Limited違約，本應每月支付25萬元月薪，但自2017年2月起停止支付薪金，要求經理人公司賠償逾150萬元。經審訊後，暫委法官藍德業今天在高等法院公佈判詞，考慮到經理人公司一方缺席聆訊，加上Ming仔證供及披露文件，藍官裁定Ming仔及其名下公司勝訴，獲賠逾151萬元。<br />\n<br />\n  法庭記者：陳子豪<br />\n<br />\n25萬月薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a6759d3692614e0d329f1493f1d0348af4d1fa","tid":2440794,"uid":40272,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:02:50.000Z","msg":"香港地越垃圾越多人工"},{"pid":"9167a11fa0898fd71b914c5d6aa3a426d2b48469","tid":2440794,"uid":41846,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:05:46.000Z","msg":"睇返咁多youtuber佢剪片係數一數二嘅<br />\n但廿五萬就見人見智啦"},{"pid":"db1f922d770078f5e262979899b908428f6ccd89","tid":2440794,"uid":3976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"58a6759d3692614e0d329f1493f1d0348af4d1fa","tid":2440794,"uid":40272,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:02:50.000Z","msg":"香港地越垃圾越多人工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:07:17.000Z","msg":"咁睇黎我係精英中既精英<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}